# Scientific plots (domain)

- Prefer helpers in `scientific_plot.py` over one-off rcParams in scripts.
- Defaults: Arial 18 pt, inward ticks, consistent legend helpers.
- After changing plot helpers or the example, run `python3 example_scientific_plot.py` and keep `example_scientific_plot.png` in sync when the visual output changes.
- Save figures with the headless-friendly path used by the example (repo-relative), not absolute machine paths.
- Agent titles for this work should use the `[domain]` prefix.
